Macao congratulates Beijing on winning 2022 Winter Olympic bid
2015-07-31 14:07:48 GMT
MACAO, July 31 (Xinhua) -- Chief Executive Chui Sai On of China 's Macao Special Administrative Region on Friday congratulated Beijing on winning the bid to host the 2022 Winter Olympic Games.In a letter, Chui said Beijing's successful bid to host the 2022 Winter Olympic Games showed the world its strength and confidence in holding international sports events.It also marked that China has taken a further step in the world sports, winning the respect and trust of the international community, Chui said. "We believe Beijing will keep its promise to make athlete- centered, sustainable and economical games in their preparations and sincerely wish 2022 Winter Olympics a great success," Chui added.Beijing beat Almaty of Kazakhstan in the IOC vote held in Kuala Lumpur, Malaysia on Friday.
